         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">19th October 1857 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ Referring to your letter of the 15th Ultimo, ¶  I have the honor to request you will forward to this Office, a description of the horse required to be sold from the Botani...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">57.10.19</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas Balmain</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 57/3301, unit 4, p. 129, VPRS 975/P1 outward registered correspondence, VA 669 Public Works Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">19th October 1857</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Referring to your letter of the 15th Ultimo,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M to D. Moore, 15 September 1857.</p>
               </note> I have the honor to request you will forward to this Office, a description of the horse required to be sold from the Botanic Gardens, in order that the necessary instructions may be given to the Auctioneer.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">(Signed) T. C. Balmain</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>For C.P.W.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Commissioner of Public Works.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dr Muëller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Director of the Botanic Gardens<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See also M to D. Moore, 23 October 1857.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
